{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01GqkuYVkkKhHmMSGZsys4eS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MrbnwZLCHebsG3tCqDb31c","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/daemon_routing.feature"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":572,"cache_read_input_tokens":13153,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":572,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PonAeiQu5NceZBvGqbs1CE","session_id":"8dacb19c-9278-40df-b484-c803ec7bbb98","uuid":"07b3063a-609f-41c7-9bc9-a4cb8855235b"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MrbnwZLCHebsG3tCqDb31c","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→Feature: Daemon Routing and Leases\n     2→  The daemon routes tasks to built-in flows, enforces task and lease invariants,\n     3→  and reconciles stale daemon state under `.ralph-burning/daemon/`.\n     4→\n     5→  # DAEMON-ROUTING-001\n     6→  Scenario: Routing precedence prefers command over labels and workspace default\n     7→    Given a daemon task with routing command \"/rb flow quick_dev\"\n     8→    And the task has routing label \"rb:flow:docs_change\"\n     9→    And the workspace default flow is \"standard\"\n    10→    When the daemon resolves task routing\n    11→    Then the selected flow is \"quick_dev\"\n    12→    And the routing source is \"command\"\n    13→\n    14→  # DAEMON-ROUTING-002\n    15→  Scenario: Valid routing labels select the flow when no command is present\n    16→    Given a daemon task with routing labels:\n    17→      | rb:flow:docs_change |\n    18→    And the workspace default flow is \"standard\"\n    19→    When the daemon resolves task routing\n    20→    Then the selected flow is \"docs_change\"\n    21→    And the routing source is \"label\"\n    22→\n    23→  # DAEMON-ROUTING-003\n    24→  Scenario: Malformed routing labels are ignored with a warning\n    25→    Given a daemon task with routing labels:\n    26→      | rb:flow          |\n    27→      | rb:flow:standard |\n    28→    When the daemon resolves task routing\n    29→    Then the selected flow is \"standard\"\n    30→    And the daemon records a routing warning\n    31→\n    32→  # DAEMON-ROUTING-004\n    33→  Scenario: Conflicting routing labels fail task creation\n    34→    Given a daemon task with routing labels:\n    35→      | rb:flow:standard   |\n    36→      | rb:flow:quick_dev  |\n    37→    When the task is created through the daemon task service\n    38→    Then task creation fails with \"AmbiguousRouting\"\n    39→\n    40→  # DAEMON-ROUTING-005\n    41→  Scenario: Duplicate non-terminal issue task is rejected\n    42→    Given a daemon task already exists for issue \"repo#101\" in status \"pending\"\n    43→    When another task is created for issue \"repo#101\"\n    44→    Then task creation fails with \"DuplicateTaskForIssue\"\n    45→\n    46→  # DAEMON-ROUTING-006\n    47→  Scenario: Lease acquisition claims the task and creates a worktree lease\n    48→    Given a pending daemon task with a valid routed flow\n    49→    When the daemon claims the task\n    50→    Then the task transitions to \"claimed\"\n    51→    And a worktree lease is persisted under \".ralph-burning/daemon/leases/\"\n    52→    And the task references the persisted lease id\n    53→\n    54→  # DAEMON-ROUTING-007\n    55→  Scenario: Reconciliation fails claimed tasks with stale leases\n    56→    Given a claimed daemon task with a stale worktree lease heartbeat\n    57→    When the user runs \"ralph-burning daemon reconcile\"\n    58→    Then the stale lease is released\n    59→    And the orphaned worktree is removed\n    60→    And the task transitions to \"failed\"\n    61→    And the failure class is \"reconciliation_timeout\"\n    62→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PonAeiQu5NceZBvGqbs1CE","session_id":"8dacb19c-9278-40df-b484-c803ec7bbb98","uuid":"fc397517-31d3-490d-b73b-1b2066126935"}
