untime_test.rs\n\n**Full Contents:** (193 lines)\n\nCore unit tests for the automation runtime:\n\n- **sample_task()** - Factory creating a minimal DaemonTask\n- **routing_resolution_prefers_command_over_label_and_default** - Command > Label > Default precedence\n- **routing_labels_ignore_malformed_values_with_warning** - \"rb:flow\" vs \"rb:flow:docs_change\"\n- **conflicting_routing_labels_fail_resolution** - Ambiguous routing error\n- **task_state_machine_accepts_expected_transitions** - Pending → Claimed → Active → Completed\n- **task_state_machine_rejects_invalid_transition** - Pending → Completed fails\n- **lease_ttl_detects_staleness** - is_stale_at checks heartbeat vs TTL\n- **worktree_path_derivation_is_deterministic** - Consistent naming scheme\n- **create_task_rejects_duplicate_active_issue** - Cannot create two non-terminal tasks for same issue\n- **retry_resets_failed_task_to_pending_and_increments_attempt_count** - Retry clears failure metadata\n\n---\n\n## File 4: /root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/requirements_drafting_test.rs (first 300 lines)\n\n**Full Contents (lines 1-300):**\n\nRequirements drafting unit tests covering:\n\n- **RequirementsRun model tests** (8 tests):\n  - new_draft/new_quick initialization\n  - is_terminal for Completed/Failed\n  - RequirementsReviewOutcome approval logic\n  - RequirementsStageId serialization round-tripping\n\n- **Contract validation tests** (18 tests):\n  - question_set accepts valid JSON\n  - Rejects duplicate question IDs, empty prompts, spaces/dots in IDs\n  - draft contract validation for empty problem_summary and goals\n  - Review outcome validation\n\nThe tests validate contracts at both schema and domain validation levels.\n\n---\n\n## File 5: /root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/daemon_lifecycle.feature\n\n**Full Contents:** (41 lines)\n\nGherkin feature file for daemon lifecycle with 5 scenarios:\n\n- **DAEMON-LIFECYCLE-001**: Daemon start with