the run to `failed` status at the question boundary (preserving `pending_question_count`) before invoking `requirements show`. Verifies show output includes pending question count (2), the \"Pending Questions:\" label, and the failure summary text.\n    12→\n    13→2. **Completion-guard scenario fidelity (Required Change #2):**\n    14→   - **SC-CR-008**: Removed the disk amendment file that previously duplicated the SC-CR-007 path. Executor now injects only a non-empty `amendment_queue.pending` in run.json with NO amendment files on disk. Verifies the completion guard fires and blocks run_completed from the snapshot-queue path alone.\n    15→\n    16→3. **SC-ROLLBACK-007 history assertion (Recommended Improvement #1):**\n    17→   - Replaced the comment-only `final_history` block with real assertions: verifies visible stage_completed count doesn't blow up with abandoned branch events, verifies `rollback_performed` event is present in history, and continues to verify `completed` status.\n    18→\n    19→## Could Not Address\n    20→- None\n    21→\n    22→## Pending Changes (Pre-Commit)\n    23→- `src/adapters/fs.rs` — seed prompt write failure injection seam\n    24→- `src/contexts/conformance_spec/scenarios.rs` — 8 executor rewrites (RD-007, RD-010, RD-011, RD-012, RD-013, RD-018, RD-021, SC-CR-008) + SC-ROLLBACK-007 assertion fix\n    25→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8dacb19c-9278-40df-b484-c803ec7bbb98","uuid":"118fc58b-fc89-4e9e-9085-fb59140228a3","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/014/20260313024631-impl-response-006.md","content":"# Implementation Response (Iteration 6)\n\n## Changes Made\n1. **Requirements scenario fidelity (Required Change #1):**\n   - **RD-007**: Added `RALPH_BURNING_TEST_SEED_PROMPT_WRITE_FAIL` env var injection seam in `fs.rs` `write_seed_pair()` that fails the prompt.md write after project.json succeeds. Executor no