sk. Verifies the completion guard fires and blocks run_completed from the snapshot-queue path alone.\n\n3. **SC-ROLLBACK-007 history assertion (Recommended Improvement #1):**\n   - Replaced the comment-only `final_history` block with real assertions: verifies visible stage_completed count doesn't blow up with abandoned branch events, verifies `rollback_performed` event is present in history, and continues to verify `completed` status.\n\n## Could Not Address\n- None\n\n## Pending Changes (Pre-Commit)\n- `src/adapters/fs.rs` — seed prompt write failure injection seam\n- `src/contexts/conformance_spec/scenarios.rs` — 8 executor rewrites (RD-007, RD-010, RD-011, RD-012, RD-013, RD-018, RD-021, SC-CR-008) + SC-ROLLBACK-007 assertion fix\n","numLines":25,"startLine":1,"totalLines":25}}}
