{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_0","type":"agent_message","text":"# Implementation Notes\n## Decisions Made\n- Fixed `watched_issue_newer_revision_after_terminal_creates_fresh_task` by removing the invalid `mark_completed` call on a `Pending` task and setting the task status directly in test setup.\n- Fixed conformance parser failures by adding required `# DAEMON-INTAKE-NNN` comment lines before each `Scenario` in `daemon_issue_intake.feature`.\n- Recorded implementation notes in `.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/016/20260313-impl-response-001.md`.\n\n## Spec Deviations\n- No intentional spec deviations were introduced.\n- The conformance feature file was updated to match the parser’s required scenario ID annotation format.\n\n## Testing\n- Full test suite passes: `372` tests passed, `0` failed.\n- Coverage included unit, CLI/E2E, and conformance suites."}}
